stify leading-8","children":"Have a session with the management team and explain about the ISO 17025 requirements, policies and objectives"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 17025 policies are developed based on continual improvement, commitment towards employees and commitment towards customers in mind."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 17025 objectives are developed on the basis of SMART technique such as specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant and Time bound."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Gap Analysis"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Mapping your existing system with the ISO 17025 requirements and analyze the gap between them. Development of a detailed gap analysis report shows the degree of compliance of existing level of operations with various clauses and requirements of ISO 17025."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 17025 Documentation"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms, ISO consultant in UAE provides assistance in preparation of the following documents as per QMS."}],["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Quality Manual"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Functional procedures / test procedures"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"System Procedures"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Functional work instructions / test instructions"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Assistance in UOM and method validation."}],["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 17025 Internal Audit"}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20"]}],"$L21"]}]}]
