1d:["$","p","31",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Final accreditation audit is done by ISO Certification bodies in UAE. Our ISO consultants in Dubai will assist your organization in closing non-conformities and after ISO 17025 audit your organization will be awarded ISO 17025 Certification in Dubai, UAE."}]
